# Local-only artifacts that must never be transferred to the buildkit context.
#
# Apple Container 0.11.0's builder-shim crashes ("unable to write data to the
# archive, code 0") on large contexts before .dockerignore is even applied —
# see https://github.com/apple/container/issues/1375 (fixed in 0.12.0). The
# real workaround in build.sh is to move these dirs aside; this file is the
# belt-and-suspenders for once the host upgrades to 0.12.x.

agent-runner/node_modules
agent-runner/dist
**/.DS_Store
